			<p>Thanks.</p>
<p>As an amature cook, I appreciate almost everything you shared, especially the salt&#8230;the one that makes me cringe is duck.</p>
<p>I have a fear of cooking duck since it seems so hard to get right&#8230;I have had it made by some top chefs and had to send it back.  Don&#8217;t know if I am ready to cook it properly.</p>
			</div>
			
